          <p class='first-para'>
            We are laughing at the hon. Lady's proposition.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0422P1_20040616_WH_42'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mrs-ann-winterton' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0422P1_20040616_WH_42' title='Link to this speech by Mrs Ann Winterton' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mrs-ann-winterton" title="Mrs Ann Winterton">Ann Winterton</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            Well, the Minister and his PPS may laugh at my proposition, but in due course people in this country may laugh at the Minister and the Government for leading them down that path. I rust that the people of the three regions involved in the referendums&#x2014;the north-west, the north-east, and Yorkshire and Humber&#x2014;will decisively vote no and reject regional government, with all its adverse financial repercussions.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <span class='time published'><a href="#2004-06-16T14:18:00Z" name="2004-06-16T14:18:00Z"><abbr class="dtstart" title="2004-06-16T14:18:00Z">2.18 pm</abbr></a></span>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0422P1_20040616_WH_44'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-michael-foster' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
