      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0422P1_20040616_WH_46'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-michael-foster' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
